---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Insights" 
  description="Thoughts, trends, and perspectives from the Digital Xceeded team. Practical insights on digital marketing, brand strategy, and technology."
>
  <section class="insights-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="hero-content">
        <span class="page-label">Insights</span>
        <h1 class="page-title">Ideas that <span class="text-gradient">move</span> business</h1>
        <p class="page-subtitle">
          Thoughts, trends, and perspectives from our team. Practical insights on digital 
          marketing, brand strategy, technology, and growth.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-bg" aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="bg-orb bg-orb-1"></div>
      <div class="bg-orb bg-orb-2"></div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Featured Article -->
  <section class="featured-section">
    <div class="container">
      <article class="featured-article reveal">
        <div class="featured-image">
          <img 
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1551434678-e076c223a692?w=1200&h=600&fit=crop" 
            alt="Team collaboration"
            loading="lazy"
          />
          <span class="featured-badge">Featured</span>
        </div>
        <div class="featured-content">
          <div class="article-meta">
            <span class="category">Strategy</span>
            <span class="date">December 2024</span>
          </div>
          <h2>The Integrated Agency Model: Why Silos Kill Results</h2>
          <p>
            In a world where brands are built across dozens of touchpoints, the traditional 
            agency model—with separate teams for brand, web, and media—creates friction 
            that hurts outcomes. Here's why integration matters.
          </p>
          <a href="/insights/integrated-agency-model" class="read-more">
            Read Article
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none">
              <path d="M3 8H13M13 8L8 3M13 8L8 13" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Article Grid -->
  <section class="articles-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="articles-grid">
        <article class="article-card reveal">
          <div class="article-image">
            <img 
              src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1460925895917-afdab827c52f?w=600&h=400&fit=crop" 
              alt="Analytics dashboard"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="article-content">
            <div class="article-meta">
              <span class="category">Analytics</span>
              <span class="date">November 2024</span>
            </div>
            <h3>Measurement in a Cookie-less World</h3>
            <p>Third-party cookies are dying. Here's how to build measurement strategies that work in the new privacy-first landscape.</p>
            <a href="/insights/cookieless-measurement" class="read-more">Read More</a>
          </div>
        </article>
        
        <article class="article-card reveal">
          <div class="article-image">
            <img 
              src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1677442136019-21780ecad995?w=600&h=400&fit=crop" 
              alt="AI visualization"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="article-content">
            <div class="article-meta">
              <span class="category">Technology</span>
              <span class="date">November 2024</span>
            </div>
            <h3>AI for Marketing: Beyond the Hype</h3>
            <p>Separating signal from noise on AI in marketing. Where it actually helps, where it falls short, and how to start smart.</p>
            <a href="/insights/ai-marketing-beyond-hype" class="read-more">Read More</a>
          </div>
        </article>
        
        <article class="article-card reveal">
          <div class="article-image">
            <img 
              src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1559136555-9303baea8ebd?w=600&h=400&fit=crop" 
              alt="Brand design"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="article-content">
            <div class="article-meta">
              <span class="category">Branding</span>
              <span class="date">October 2024</span>
            </div>
            <h3>When to Rebrand (And When Not To)</h3>
            <p>Rebranding is expensive and risky. Here's our framework for deciding whether a rebrand will drive growth or just burn budget.</p>
            <a href="/insights/when-to-rebrand" class="read-more">Read More</a>
          </div>
        </article>
        
        <article class="article-card reveal">
          <div class="article-image">
            <img 
              src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1551288049-bebda4e38f71?w=600&h=400&fit=crop" 
              alt="Performance dashboard"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="article-content">
            <div class="article-meta">
              <span class="category">Performance</span>
              <span class="date">October 2024</span>
            </div>
            <h3>Website Speed: The Hidden Revenue Driver</h3>
            <p>Every second of load time costs you conversions. Here's how to diagnose and fix performance issues that hurt revenue.</p>
            <a href="/insights/website-speed-revenue" class="read-more">Read More</a>
          </div>
        </article>
        
        <article class="article-card reveal">
          <div class="article-image">
            <img 
              src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1552664730-d307ca884978?w=600&h=400&fit=crop" 
              alt="Team workshop"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="article-content">
            <div class="article-meta">
              <span class="category">Process</span>
              <span class="date">September 2024</span>
            </div>
            <h3>The Discovery Process: Why It Matters</h3>
            <p>Great projects start with great discovery. Here's how we structure the discovery phase to set projects up for success.</p>
            <a href="/insights/discovery-process" class="read-more">Read More</a>
          </div>
        </article>
        
        <article class="article-card reveal">
          <div class="article-image">
            <img 
              src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1533750516457-a7f992034fec?w=600&h=400&fit=crop" 
              alt="Social media"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="article-content">
            <div class="article-meta">
              <span class="category">Social</span>
              <span class="date">September 2024</span>
            </div>
            <h3>B2B Social: What Actually Works</h3>
            <p>B2B brands often struggle with social. Here's what we've learned about creating content that builds pipeline.</p>
            <a href="/insights/b2b-social-strategy" class="read-more">Read More</a>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Newsletter -->
  <section class="newsletter-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="newsletter-content reveal">
        <h2>Stay in the loop</h2>
        <p>Get insights delivered to your inbox. No spam, just useful perspectives on digital strategy, brand, and growth.</p>
        <form class="newsletter-form">
          <input type="email" placeholder="Your email address" required />
          <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Subscribe</button>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .insights-hero {
    position: relative;
    padding: calc(var(--header-height) + var(--space-4xl)) 0 var(--space-3xl);
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--color-white) 0%, var(--color-cream) 100%);
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  
  .hero-content {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }
  
  .page-label {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }
  
  .page-title {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }
  
  .page-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  
  .hero-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  
  .bg-orb {
    position: absolute;
    border-radius: 50%;
    filter: blur(80px);
    opacity: 0.4;
  }
  
  .bg-orb-1 {
    width: 500px;
    height: 500px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 87, 87, 0.3) 0%, rgba(255, 152, 0, 0.2) 100%);
    top: -200px;
    right: -100px;
  }
  
  .bg-orb-2 {
    width: 400px;
    height: 400px;
    background: rgba(255, 152, 0, 0.2);
    bottom: -150px;
    left: -100px;
  }
  
  /* Featured */
  .featured-section {
    padding: var(--space-4xl) 0;
    background: var(--color-cream);
  }
  
  .featured-article {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-3xl);
    align-items: center;
    background: var(--color-white);
    border-radius: var(--radius-2xl);
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  
  .featured-image {
    position: relative;
  }
  
  .featured-image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    aspect-ratio: 2/1;
  }
  
  .featured-badge {
    position: absolute;
    top: var(--space-lg);
    left: var(--space-lg);
    background: var(--gradient-warm);
    color: white;
    padding: var(--space-xs) var(--space-md);
    border-radius: var(--radius-full);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  
  .featured-content {
    padding: var(--space-2xl);
  }
  
  .article-meta {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }
  
  .category {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }
  
  .date {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
  }
  
  .featured-content h2 {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    line-height: 1.3;
  }
  
  .featured-content p {
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }
  
  .read-more {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    transition: gap var(--transition-base);
  }
  
  .read-more:hover {
    gap: var(--space-md);
  }
  
  /* Articles */
  .articles-section {
    padding: var(--space-5xl) 0;
    background: var(--color-white);
  }
  
  .articles-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-xl);
  }
  
  .article-card {
    background: var(--color-cream);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: all var(--transition-base);
  }
  
  .article-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
  }
  
  .article-image img {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 3/2;
    object-fit: cover;
  }
  
  .article-content {
    padding: var(--space-lg);
  }
  
  .article-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
    line-height: 1.3;
  }
  
  .article-card p {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }
  
  /* Newsletter */
  .newsletter-section {
    padding: var(--space-5xl) 0;
    background: var(--color-text);
  }
  
  .newsletter-content {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    color: var(--color-white);
  }
  
  .newsletter-content h2 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }
  
  .newsletter-content p {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }
  
  .newsletter-form {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    max-width: 450px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  
  .newsletter-form input {
    flex: 1;
    padding: var(--space-md) var(--space-lg);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    color: white;
    font-size: 1rem;
  }
  
  .newsletter-form input::placeholder {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .featured-article {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    
    .articles-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .articles-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    
    .newsletter-form {
      flex-direction: column;
    }
  }
</style>
